  title: How do you prevent recursion infinite loops?
  text: "By adding some parameter and some condition that eventually stops the recursive
    loop.\n##REF##code,\r\nprivate void RunRecursionXTimes(int x) {\r\n    if (x
    <= 0) {\r\n        return;\r\n    } else {\r\n        RunRecursionXTimes(x -
    1);\r\n    }\n}\r\n---------\r\nRunRecursionXTimes(3); // This will run the recursive
    code 3 times\r\n##REF##"
